      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/keygen-key-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "先挑两个素数 p 和 q，把它们相乘得到模数 n。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "keygen",
      "line_id": "key-2",
      "filename": "keygen-key-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/keygen-key-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.76,
      "size": 28224,
      "text": "再算出欧拉函数 φ，等于 p 减一乘以 q 减一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "keygen",
      "line_id": "key-3",
      "filename": "keygen-key-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/keygen-key-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "选一个与 φ 互质的数 e 做公钥，它的模逆 d 就是私钥。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "encrypt",
      "line_id": "enc-1",
      "filename": "encrypt-enc-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/encrypt-enc-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25056,
      "text": "把消息写成一个数字 m，用公钥做加密。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "encrypt",
      "line_id": "enc-2",
      "filename": "encrypt-enc-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/encrypt-enc-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26784,
      "text": "计算 m 的 e 次方再对 n 取余，得到密文 c。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "encrypt",
      "line_id": "enc-3",
      "filename": "encrypt-enc-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/encrypt-enc-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "这一步谁都能算，因为公钥 e 和模数 n 是公开的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "decrypt",
      "line_id": "dec-1",
